When it falls, it bends and breaks, and the fragments are stretched or rotated, creating cracks between them.

149
00:23:05,840 --> 00:23:08,840
This is how rock creep occurs.

150
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:16,840
On a gentle slope, gravity causes it to shift downward, and over a long period of time, the soil gradually accumulates.

